{"tid":1768430,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我們不退後 才會有然後","createTime":"2019-12-04T05:12:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-04T05:48:07.000Z","uid":222018,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"6e7a374bf8504de39bbecafdbfb3872e890ef3e4","tid":1768430,"uid":222018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T05:12:47.000Z","msg":"區選大勝之後休息成個星期<br />\n成個熱門都冇行動post<br />\n<br />\n12.1勿忘初心大遊行超級和平<br />\n換黎既又係TG同黑警打人<br />\n<br />\n政府繼續佢有佢做 警謊繼續胡說八道 <br />\n<br />\n既然決定set左死線係12.8要仆街政府回應五大訴求 <br />\n咁12.7係咪應該出下街<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n休息佐成個星期<br />\n死線前全力chur盡佢！<br />\n<br />\n佢繼續唔理我地就12.9三罷 <br />\n死線前真係冇休息既餘地呀手足！<br />\n<br />\n利申：次次都有出去發夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eTirrE0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeTirrE0.jpg&h=6432f540&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WfWMrE1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWfWMrE1.jpg&h=c38f7763&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dTvtEZ1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdTvtEZ1.jpg&h=5af8b887&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eeAUAyn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeeAUAyn.jpg&h=042a1db1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kNtrrE3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkNtrrE3.jpg&h=3dc98bcd&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e7a21f6e33c0ad5b31261c39e9d738f9ff527a34","tid":1768430,"uid":249263,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-04T05:13:41.000Z","msg":"(twitter要人）意大利議會 外務委員會 支持香港, 要求歐盟調查香港警暴<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1768418\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1768418</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8e0213de4f78f26cb37d6a20e238516d862099ed","tid":1768430,"uid":222018,"like":0,"disl